ggle="dropdown"  ><span style="cursor:pointer" class="caret"></span></span><ul class="dropdown-menu"><li><a>FORMATO VERTICAL</a> <a href="<?php echo base_url("printings/print_estudios/$historial_id/$row->id_i_e/1/vert/$row->centro") ?>"style="cursor:pointer;color:#000"target="_blank">con la foto</a> <a href="<?php echo base_url("printings/print_estudios/$historial_id/$row->id_i_e/0/vert/$row->centro") ?>"style="cursor:pointer;color:#000"target="_blank">Sin la foto</a></li><li><a>FORMATO HORIZONTAL</a> <a href="<?php echo base_url("printings/print_estudios/$historial_id/$row->id_i_e/1/horiz/$row->centro") ?>"style="cursor:pointer;color:#000"target="_blank">con la foto</a> <a href="<?php echo base_url("printings/print_estudios/$historial_id/$row->id_i_e/0/horiz/$row->centro") ?>"style="cursor:pointer;color:#000"target="_blank">Sin la foto</a></li></ul></li></ul></td><?php }else{echo "<i style='color:red' class='fa fa-ban'></i>";} ?><td><?php if($row->operator==$user_id||$perfil=="Admin"){ ?><a class="delete-estudio"style="cursor:pointer"title="Eliminar estudio<?=$row->estudio?>"id="<?=$row->id_i_e?>"><i class="fa fa-remove"style="color:red"></i></a><?php }else{echo "<i style='color:red' class='fa fa-ban'></i>";} ?></td></tr><?php } ?></tbody></table><div class="fade modal"id="edit_estudios"role="dialog"><div class="modal-dialog modal-lg"><div class="modal-content"></div></div></div><div class="fade modal"id="print_estudio_foto"role="dialog"><div class="modal-dialog modal-xs"><div class="modal-content"></div></div></div><div class="fade modal"id="print_estudio_foto_oriz"role="dialog"><div class="modal-dialog modal-xs"><div class="modal-content"></div></div></div><script>$("#print_estudio_foto").on("hidden.bs.modal",function(){$(this).removeData("bs.modal")}),$("#print_estudio_foto_oriz").on("hidden.bs.modal",function(){$(this).removeData("bs.modal")}),$("#edit_estudios").on("hidden.bs.modal",function(){$(this).removeData("bs.modal"),allEstudios()}),$(".delete-estudio")